<tr>
<td style="padding: 0px 20px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; border-left: 1px solid #cccccc; border-right: 1px solid #cccccc;" valign="top">
<p><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 26px; color: #0079c1; font-weight: bold;">You can help increase funding for NMDP/Be The Match’s mission</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 20px;">The NMDP/Be The Match needs your help to encourage Congress to maintain its commitment to individuals who need a life-saving bone marrow or cord blood transplant by increasing the funding levels and expanding the registry.</span></p>
<p><a style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #0079c1;" href="#">Learn why your support is important and how you can help</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- END Story 5 -->
<!-- START Story 6 -->
<tr>
<td style="padding: 0px 20px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; border: 1px solid #cccccc;" align="left" valign="top">
<p><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 26px; color: #0079c1; font-weight: bold;">Medicare to expand HCT coverage for sickle cell disease, multiple myeloma, and myelofibrosis</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 20px;">The Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) has released its final decision to expand national coverage for allogeneic HCT for patients with sickle cell disease, multiple myeloma, and myelofibrosis within the context of Coverage with Evidence Development (CED).</span></p>
<p><a style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 20px; text-decoration: none; color: #0079c1;" href="#">Learn more about CED coverage expansion and what it will mean for patients</a></p>
</td>
</tr>
